  "prompt": "What talents do Enneagram type 2 people have?",
  "response": "Enneagram Type 2 individuals, often called \"The Helper\" or \"The Giver,\" typically have several notable talents:\n\n1. Interpersonal Skills\n- Exceptional empathy\n- Strong ability to connect with others\n- Excellent emotional intelligence\n- Natural caregiving abilities\n\n2. Relationship-Building\n- Highly supportive of friends and family\n- Skilled at nurturing relationships\n- Good at making people feel valued and understood\n\n3. Emotional Awareness\n- Intuitive about others' emotional needs\n- Highly perceptive of underlying feelings\n- Skilled at providing emotional support\n\n4. Communication\n- Warm and engaging conversationalists\n- Good listeners\n- Able to offer compassionate advice\n\n5. Altruism\n- Genuinely enjoy helping others\n- Willing to make personal sacrifices\n- Strong sense of generosity\n\n6. Problem-Solving in Relationships\n- Adept at mediating conflicts\n- Skilled at finding solutions that consider everyone's feelings\n- Able to create harmony in group settings\n\n7. Emotional Support\n- Provide comfort and reassurance\n- Create safe emotional environments\n- Offer genuine care and concern\n\nThese talents make Type 2s valuable friends, partners, colleagues, and community members who excel in nurturing and supportive roles.",
